<h2 id="conclusion">Conclusion</h2>

<p>NAS rigs are great mass storage replacements for external hard drives, and buying a good NAS case is a great way to save money too.</p>

<p>Building your own NAS is a bit more time consuming than buying a prebuilt NAS, but that doesn‚Äôt mean you shouldn‚Äôt do it.</p>

<p>You‚Äôll save money, learn how your NAS works and hell, you may even have some fun.</p>
